request.description:
Breed two monsters together

Request Body:
- parent1Id: ID of the first parent monster
- parent2Id: ID of the second parent monster

Response:
- 201: Offspring created successfully
- 400: Invalid input
- 404: One or both parent monsters not found
- 401: Unauthorized (missing or invalid token)

Example Test Script:
```javascript
// Get two monster IDs from environment variables
const parent1Id = pm.environment.get('monster1_id');
const parent2Id = pm.environment.get('monster2_id');

// Set the request body
pm.request.body.raw = JSON.stringify({
    parent1Id: parent1Id,
    parent2Id: parent2Id
});

// Test the response
pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {
    pm.response.to.have.status(201);
});

pm.test('Response has monster data', function () {
    const response = pm.response.json();
    pm.expect(response.data).to.have.property('monster');
    pm.expect(response.data.monster).to.have.property('name');
    pm.expect(response.data.monster).to.have.property('parent1');
    pm.expect(response.data.monster).to.have.property('parent2');
    pm.expect(response.data.monster).to.have.property('generation');
});
```
